00:24:31.650 --> 00:24:32.950
to content with this violence

00:24:32.950 --> 00:24:34.890
in a completely different
and unsettling way.

00:24:34.890 --> 00:24:38.240
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Right,
right, right.

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:39.540
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: A
lot of the violence

00:24:39.540 --> 00:24:40.840
in your poems is
linked to racism.

00:24:40.840 --> 00:24:45.080
