00:34:57.780 --> 00:34:59.750
like sort of realizing that,

00:34:59.750 --> 00:35:01.870
the way that memory,
I think, I think.

00:35:01.870 --> 00:35:07.140
The way that memory gets
sort of conjured out of that,

00:35:07.140 --> 00:35:15.270
that sense of like, oh, that,
