00:35:19.910 --> 00:35:21.210
really remarkable.

00:35:21.210 --> 00:35:22.510
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Sanctified.

00:35:22.510 --> 00:35:24.680
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Sanctified,
yeah, totally, totally.

00:35:24.680 --> 00:35:25.980
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: In the poem.

00:35:25.980 --> 00:35:27.280
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Yeah, yeah.

00:35:27.280 --> 00:35:29.880
And I think it's probably, I'm
realizing that in the course

00:35:29.880 --> 00:35:35.310
of writing it, like
trying to, yeah, yeah.

00:35:35.310 --> 00:35:38.430
Something like that.

00:35:38.430 --> 00:35:40.680
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: That
little factory in your head,

00:35:40.680 --> 00:35:44.240
the factory where loss makes
all things beautiful grow.

00:35:44.240 --> 00:35:45.540
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Yeah.

00:35:45.540 --> 00:35:49.110
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: That's
the poetic function.

00:35:49.110 --> 00:35:50.410
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Yeah.

00:35:50.410 --> 00:35:54.000
Yeah. Now I don't think only
