01:03:47.170 --> 01:03:48.470
&gt;&gt; Ross Gay: Great.

01:03:48.470 --> 01:03:50.930
It's called Thank You.

01:03:50.930 --> 01:03:55.110
If you find yourself
half naked and barefoot

01:03:55.110 --> 01:04:00.400
in the frosty grass, hearing
again the earth's great sonorous

01:04:00.400 --> 01:04:04.810
moan that says, you are the
air of the now and gone,

01:04:04.810 --> 01:04:08.810
that says all you love will turn
to dust and will meet you there.

01:04:08.810 --> 01:04:11.640
Do not raise your fist.

01:04:11.640 --> 01:04:14.040
Do not raise your
small voice against it.

01:04:14.040 --> 01:04:17.260
And do not take cover.

01:04:17.260 --> 01:04:20.820
Instead, curl your
goes into the grass,

01:04:20.820 --> 01:04:24.300
watch the cloud ascending
from your lips.

01:04:24.300 --> 01:04:27.450
Walk through the
garden's dormant splendor.

01:04:27.450 --> 01:04:30.220
Say only thank you.

01:04:30.220 --> 01:04:31.520
Thank you.

